    <del:text>- the report by Fernando Navarrete Rojas, on behalf of the Committee on Economic and Monetary Affairs, on the European Semester for economic policy coordination 2025 (2024/2112(INI)) (A10-0022/2025); and.
- the report by Maravillas Abadía Jover, on behalf of the Committee on Employment and Social Affairs, on the European Semester for economic policy coordination: employment and social priorities for 2025 (2024/2084(INI)) (A10-0023-2025).</del:text>
    <del:timestamp rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2025-03-12T09:01:21</del:timestamp>
